ing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">目标管理：</span></strong>凡事需要有目标，才会有坚持！七个人物法，教你快速找到学习榜样。<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">目标建立、目标分解，迅速学会。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">效率管理：</span></strong>效率在于专注力，避免注意力分散<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">与拖延症</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">，萌姐有妙招！</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">健康管理：</span></strong>控制好能量来源，控制好情绪管理。通过呼吸法、香薰法等调解健康系统。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px; line-height: 1.2; background-color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border: 2px solid rgb(142, 99, 82); padding: 2px 8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: -7px 5px; color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">订阅须知</p></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><stro