le="box-sizing: border-box;">②功能语言学和脑认知心理学博士</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">③<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">4次</span>出席<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">APEC CEO峰会</span>，<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">3次</span>参加<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">达沃斯世界经济论坛</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">④</strong><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2次</span></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">被</span></strong></span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">博鳌亚洲论坛<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">授予“全球青年领袖”</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">⑤成为<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">立德领导力创始人</span>，</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">“极北咖啡”创始人，下班加油站APP创始人，早起文创、美妆、生活消费品电商创始人</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">⑥<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">30岁</span>的张萌<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">登上纽约时代广场</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">⑦被<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">30国</span>元首接见</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">⑧行走了<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">40个国家</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">⑨<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">畅销书作家</span>，连续出版6本书</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">她，就是<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">张萌</span></strong>，一个目标明确且行动力极强的女子。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; color: rgb(59, 58, 58); font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">作为早起提倡者，</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">早起这件事她已经坚持了18年</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">每天清晨4点半，在大部分人还在享受美梦时，她已经在微博上早起打卡了。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">很多人问早起做什么？</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">她说早起要修炼硬本领，只有早起时光只属于自己。</span></strong>我们来算算，工作8小时是属于公司、属于老板的；睡眠至少还要6-7小时，那么剩下来的时间里除了吃饭、娱乐、休闲等陪家人、陪朋友的时间，你还剩多少时间呢？细思极恐，有木有？</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">因此，张萌才说早起时间格外重要。在2017年的早起时间里，她不但完成了100多本书籍的阅读，还完成了3本书的写作。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">你可能惊讶于她的自制力，但她却认为<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">“当你明白为什么要早起，并知道早起做什么且能做到，那么世界就变了”</span></strong>。她说，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">“我很不认同意一种说法——人每天被‘梦想’叫醒。我们每天应该是被‘目标’叫醒”。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; color: rgb(59, 58, 58); font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">学渣变学霸，</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">她竟然是被这件事点燃</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如此自律的一个人，你可能完全无法想象，她曾经也是个放学不拿书包、一门心思玩游戏的学渣。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">提到学渣玩游戏，萌姐明显有一丝愧疚地讲了一个小故事：由于玩游戏，萌姐的母亲大人发过一次火，气冲冲地就把电脑显示器给砸了，而此时，张萌竟然语不惊人死不休地说了句“妈，真要砸电脑你砸显示器是没有用的，得砸主机呀！”</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">就是这么一个略叛逆、自我的小女孩，现在看来是N头牛都拉不回来的人，到底受了什么启发呢？用萌姐的话讲，这个<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">决定性瞬间是去做老师口中的“北京奥运会志愿者”，因为这能为国争光。</span></strong>这件事情瞬间将张萌点燃了！</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">这也是萌姐目标管理的初次尝试——做了结果倒推，要做奥运会志愿者，那就必须考个好大学；考个好大学，就必须上个好高中；上个好高中，那就要从初中起好好学习。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">从此，萌姐就走上了学霸之路。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; color: rgb(59, 58, 58); font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">退学浙大，</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">为目标开启1000天小树林计划</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">费心费力考上了浙江大学，但北京奥运会志愿者却不在此招生。一直以来激励自己的动力（去做北京奥运会志愿者）破碎了，张萌的韧性再次体现出来。她选择毅然退学，从一个理科生改为文科生，历时一年时间考上了北京师范大学英语系。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">初入大学，张萌的成绩并不是很好。此时想做外交官的她，想的是只有做到年级第一才能离目标更近一点。于是，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">她开启了1000天小树林计划和10000小时的刻意练习。</span></strong>大学四年，从不间断。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">结果可想而知，张萌又一次从“学渣”升级为学霸，成为年级第一，拥有了外交机会。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">她，再一次实现了她的目标。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; color: rgb(59, 58, 58); font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">坚信坚持的力量，</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">英国前首相卡梅伦也为她背书</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">张萌的自律能力如她的眼神一样坚定。她常说的一句话，就是<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">“坚信坚持的力量”。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">不论是初中的奋起直追，还是大学的1000天小树林计划，她都在践行着“坚持”二字。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如今的张萌，与联想控股董事会主席柳传志、百度总裁张亚勤、Uber优步CEO同为博鳌亚洲论坛发言嘉宾，行走超过30个国家。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">并且，四次参加APEC CEO峰会，受到李克强总理、副主席李源潮、政协主席俞正声，法国总理瓦尔斯、前任总理拉法兰，美国前国务卿希拉里、基辛格，英国前首相卡梅伦、布朗，新加坡总统纳丹，新西兰前总理Jenny SHIPLEY等近30位国家领导人接见，探讨国际青年发展问题。英国前首相卡梅伦更有书评“把最好的祝福送给青年们”。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">面对不同领域的头部人物，张萌也采取着<span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“以人为师”</strong></span>的行动力，并提出<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">“7个人物法”</span></strong>，来领导自己以及青年人快速寻找学习的目标与方向。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; color: rgb(59, 58, 58); font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">致力于青年领导力推广，</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">架起一座大学与企业之间的桥梁</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">作为立德领导力的创始人，张萌要打造一个推广青年领导力的公益组织，让企业省心，让大学生不迷茫、不小白。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2017年，一篇名为《你20多岁时的生活方式，决定了30岁的打开方式》登上了《人民日报》以及近千家自媒体账号，引发近2亿人次阅读量。文中描述了张萌的时间管理理念，以及自我管理方法，并引领拥有自我驱动力的青年，完成从零到一，实现梦想的过程。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">“架起一座大学与企业之间的桥梁”</span></strong>，这是张萌建立立德的初心。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如果你是对自己有所要求的人，那么张萌老师的《张萌：高效能人士的自我管理》这堂课将告诉你最直接的方法！注意，这不是鸡血或鸡汤，而是真正可操作的实用方法。</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px; line-height: 1.2; background-color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border: 2px solid rgb(142, 99, 82); padding: 2px 8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: -7px 5px; color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">课程介绍</p></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">时间管理：</span></strong>早起帮你拥有更多时间，早起不是无所事事，你需要发现目标并且去做。学会目标分解和单点突破发，助你有效管理时间。时间管理不只属于牛人，小白同样需要。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">目标管理：</span></strong>凡事需要有目标，才会有坚持！七个人物法，教你快速找到学习榜样。<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">目标建立、目标分解，迅速学会。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">效率管理：</span></strong>效率在于专注力，避免注意力分散<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">与拖延症</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">，萌姐有妙招！</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">健康管理：</span></strong>控制好能量来源，控制好情绪管理。通过呼吸法、香薰法等调解健康系统。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px; line-height: 1.2; background-color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border: 2px solid rgb(142, 99, 82); padding: 2px 8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: -7px 5px; color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">订阅须知</p></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1.课程概况：</span></strong></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">《张萌：高效能人士的自我管理》为<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;">149元音频产品（有效期：2017.12.15-2019.12.14）</span>。本产品包为虚拟服务内容，<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(240, 153, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">一经订阅成功概不退款</strong></span>，请您理解。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2.更新方式：<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"></span></span></strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;">每周一更新一节课，共计10期（约450分钟）内容。</span></span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">订阅后，即可<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(240, 153, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">一次性解锁</strong></span>该产品包内全部内容。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;">3.收听平台：</span></strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">此平台购买的产品<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(240, 153, 0); box-sizing: border-box;">只可在此平台收听</span></strong>。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(142, 99, 82); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">4.购买方式：</strong></span>自己学，则点击屏幕下<span style="color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;">方<span style=" box-sizing: borde